Generally, the code is released as an All Rights Reserved; in the event that it becomes invalid, please note the owner's wishes:

The code is released in order to aid in integration with other systems and for educational use, not for the project to be continued in a different name or under the same namy by another team.

Source and Binaries are provided with the hopes that they will be helpful, but they are primarily developed for Betterverse's specific needs and may not work well in all environments.